Sun Pharmaceutical Rises After U.S. FDA Resolves Warning Letter

-- B y   H a r i   G o v i n d
-- 
2011-09-19T03:47:25Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-19/sun-pharmaceutical-rises-after-u-s-fda-resolves-warning-letter.html
Sun Pharmaceutical Industries Ltd. (SUNP) ,
 India ’s biggest drugmaker by market value, rose as much as 2.3
percent in Mumbai after saying the U.S.  Food and Drug
Administration  has resolved its warning letter after re-
inspecting the company’s manufacturing facility in  New Jersey .  The shares rose 1.5 percent to 493.3 rupees at 9:16 a.m.
local time.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Hari Govind at 
 hgovind@bloomberg.net  